1
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:20,940
=About Love=

2
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:31,790 --> 00:01:33,480
(An Miu)
Bei, I'm here!

4
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:41,340
(Zhen Guan)

5
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:53,590
Bei...

6
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,680
An Miu,

7
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,070
I asked you here today

8
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,150
because I have a few questions for you.

9
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:05,200
I hope you'll answer me honestly.

10
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:14,240
Did you go to Guan

11
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,310
to have her test Lin Chen?

12
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,430
Did you only give her Lin Chen's name,

13
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,120
or did you tell her everything about

14
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,150
my past with him?

15
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,030
Does that even matter?

16
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:33,470
Answer me.

17
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,310
She did ask a lot of questions.

18
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:40,750
Otherwise, she wouldn't have taken the job.

19
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,680
So you did mention my name.

20
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:48,750
Yeah.

21
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:51,430
What's wrong?

22
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:52,430
Second question.

23
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,590
We've known each other for years.

24
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:58,150
I just need one honest answer from you.

25
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,360
I'll take your word for it.

26
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,000
What's with the photos?

27
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,710
They were just doing hypnotherapy.

28
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:27,190
They kept the windows open the whole time.

29
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,520
After Li Xiaoxi fell asleep,

30
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,430
Lin Chen walked to the window,

31
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,590
sat down, drank coffee,

32
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,870
and looked at the view.

33
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:37,470
Even if I let it slip,

34
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,680
and Guan set the whole thing up,

35
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,150
she did do the test.

36
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,750
Isn't that solid proof?

37
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,190
It wasn't the only time they dated.

38
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,360
They even went to see a movie together.

39
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,240
I didn't get photos.

40
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,590
Who knows what they did?

41
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,190
If she's really got nothing to hide,

42
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,120
why didn't she tell you anything?

43
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,520
Now you've got to come ask me.

44
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:58,080
In my opinion, at least psychologically,

45
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,240
this proves

46
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,800
she's dependent on relationship tests...

47
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,680
Alright, An Miu.

48
00:04:02,090 --> 00:04:02,960
I've told you to

49
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,190
stay out of Lin Chen's business.

50
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,000
I won't let anything
come between Li Xiaoxi and me.

51
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,840
Do you understand?

52
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:09,150
Isn't this all because of her?

53
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:10,400
Why are you defending her?

54
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,360
But I've told you over and over.

55
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,750
Just stay out of it.

56
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:15,240
Why won't you listen?

57
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,630
We agreed on investigating

58
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,600
Lin Chen, didn't we?

59
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,390
Now that Li Xiaoxi is involved,

60
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,630
you think it's all my fault.

61
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,160
It was just me.

62
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,800
I was being delusional.

63
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:28,160
Do I deserve this just because I like you?

64
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,000
What does that

65
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,600
have to do with all that?

66
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,120
I told you we can't be together.

67
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,870
I see you as my sister. You know that.

68
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,310
I'm willing to give you everything,

69
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,870
yet in your eyes,

70
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,600
I'm still worse than that liar.

71
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:53,310
I do like you.

72
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,830
Is that why I deserve

73
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:56,270
to be trampled on by you?

74
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,000
I'm the biggest fool

75
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,160
for falling for you!

76
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,830
Ningxia Tan Mutton,

77
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:38,510
roasted with Xinjiang cumin and Xi'an chili.

78
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,120
No wonder you're the boss.

79
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,000
You know how to play the game.

80
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,680
You've got a sharp nose.

81
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,750
Maybe you should keep quiet.

82
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,560
You're here for some enlightenment?

83
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,440
Look at you.

84
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:55,000
Besides chatting people up,

85
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,070
what else can you do?

86
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,560
Listen to yourself.

87
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,270
I guess those skewers aren't

88
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,240
going to sit well with me.

89
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,480
Why is that?

90
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,390
They'll give you the runs?

91
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:09,560
Talking to someone
as unrefined as you, one can't even

92
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,070
use a figure of speech.

93
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,120
Why would you even need one for that?

94
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,040
That's just reinventing the wheel.

95
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,040
You've being snarky lately,

96
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,240
starting to sound

97
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:22,430
more and more like me.

98
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,190
Are you and Li Xiaoxi

99
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,160
still in a cold war?

100
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,590
How did you know?

101
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:38,630
I can tell.

102
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,750
Being a master of
serialized romance comics has to

103
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,760
count for something.

104
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,240
I'm over it now.

105
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:50,750
It's no big deal.

106
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,630
I'll go back later.

107
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,800
I helped you see the light.

108
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,680
I've thought it over,

109
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,120
and I see everything

110
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,390
for what it really is.

111
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,600
I acted on impulse that day.

112
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,680
Li Xiaoxi must've been terrified.

113
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,150
There you go.

114
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,600
It's just a couple's spat.

115
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,430
Why let it last overnight?

116
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,750
Don't mess up and drive her away.

117
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,840
You're right.

118
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,110
What is it?

119
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:29,070
If you've got a problem with me, just say it.

120
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:30,680
Don't take it out on my food.

121
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,080
What's wrong?

122
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,560
Are you okay?

123
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,560
This is all your fault.

124
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,000
I'm not okay at all!

125
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:51,390
This barbecue isn't fresh.

126
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,190
How come I'm fine after eating it?

127
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,120
You barely touched it!

128
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:03,510
Maybe I should reflect on

129
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:04,950
exactly how I offended you.

130
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,070
Think long and hard about it.

131
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,110
Screw that.

132
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,950
(You fall in love)

133
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:30,310
(not because she's beautiful or tall,)

134
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,080
(but because the sun was shining,)

135
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,440
(and she wore a white shirt.)

136
00:08:37,730 --> 00:08:41,240
♪There's nothing that I wouldn't try to do♪

137
00:08:41,250 --> 00:08:45,800
♪For this feeling to have you♪

138
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,510
Oh my God. You...

139
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,870
What skewers did you get me? God...

140
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,030
Enjoy. I gotta go.

141
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,320
You can't just torment me and dip!

142
00:08:57,330 --> 00:09:00,720
♪For an image of you♪

143
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:03,710
♪Take my hand again♪

144
00:09:03,930 --> 00:09:05,790
♪Take my mind again♪

145
00:09:06,010 --> 00:09:09,100
♪Break it to my heart again♪

146
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:11,600
♪I'm falling out again♪

147
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:13,620
♪I'm on my knees again♪

148
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:18,220
♪To beg for the truth♪

149
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:22,990
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

150
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:28,080
♪Is that the secret to love♪

151
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:31,750
♪I thought it had came from below us♪

152
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:35,020
♪Did it come from above♪

153
00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:38,920
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

154
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:44,010
♪Is it a push or a shove♪

155
00:09:44,570 --> 00:09:47,887
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

156
00:09:47,901 --> 00:09:51,040
♪This secret of love♪

157
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:53,820
♪I'm addicted♪

158
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:58,180
♪Every second of the day♪

159
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:03,380
♪Walking round the corners of the room♪

160
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:07,700
♪Chasing your shadows♪

161
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,780
♪When the curtains close♪

162
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,820
♪I'll still be loving you♪

163
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:15,020
♪Sinking deep and deeper again♪

164
00:10:15,780 --> 00:10:17,660
♪When the oceans fall♪

165
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:19,540
♪I'll still be holding you♪

166
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:23,220
♪Cause you are my truth♪

167
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:27,260
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

168
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:32,020
♪Is that the secret to love♪

169
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:35,740
♪I thought it had came from below us♪

170
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:39,220
♪Did it come from above♪

171
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:43,060
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

172
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:47,940
♪Is it a push or a shove♪

173
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:51,580
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

174
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:56,220
♪This secret of love♪

175
00:10:57,340 --> 00:11:00,420
♪There's no more reason to fight it♪

176
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:04,700
♪There's no more reason to lie again♪

177
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:12,540
♪There's no more reason to run away and hide♪

178
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:17,980
♪I'll admit♪

179
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:22,460
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

180
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:27,420
♪There's nothing that I wouldn't try to do♪

181
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:34,420
♪For this feeling to have you♪

182
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:39,190
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

183
00:11:39,190 --> 00:11:44,330
♪Is it a push or a shove♪

184
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:47,900
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

185
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:51,630
♪This secret of love♪

186
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,390
Easy does it.

187
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,280
Steady...

188
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:00,870
Watch your step.

189
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,080
You don't have to treat me like a patient.

190
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,120
I didn't break any bones.

191
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:08,870
But you should be careful.

192
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:10,390
Try not to get the wounds wet.

193
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:13,720
I'll pick you up tonight.
What are you in the mood for?

194
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,910
I don't know whether to feel happy,

195
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:19,080
or just sad.

196
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,680
How come?

197
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,030
I'm happy because

198
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,200
you've never been this kind to me.

199
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:27,510
But I'm sad because

200
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,550
I know it's just out of guilt.

201
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,870
Do you have to analyze someone all the time?

202
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,040
Aren't you tired?

203
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:35,510
Sorry.

204
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:38,000
I guess I just don't
want to live that clear-headed.

205
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,960
Anyway, he's the one who hit me.

206
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,440
You don't have to do this for him.

207
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,870
I'm not entirely innocent.

208
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,120
If I'd spoken up sooner,

209
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,790
and just talked to him instead of sulking,

210
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,720
you wouldn't have been dragged into this.

211
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,320
So you finally admit it.

212
00:12:58,270 --> 00:13:00,390
You never wanted me involved at all.

213
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:03,030
I was just a tool for you
to vent your frustration.

214
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,960
No, that's not what I meant.

215
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,910
I'm kidding.

216
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,120
We made a deal, remember?

217
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,670
Be true to ourselves.

218
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,790
Since you've figured it all out,

219
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,270
it's not too late to make things clear.

220
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,630
These bruises of mine are proof

221
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:21,550
that he's still waiting

222
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:24,240
for an explanation from you.

223
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,390
Take a step forward.

224
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:29,550
Go meet Bei.

225
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,790
No need to pick me up tonight.

226
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,160
I'm going to be busy.

227
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:48,540
(Guan)

228
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:54,920
Miss An,

229
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:56,910
can I help you with something?

230
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,630
As if you didn't know.

231
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,960
Bei has forgiven Li Xiaoxi.

232
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,030
They're back together.

233
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:05,360
Oh?

234
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,200
So soon?

235
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:08,080
I don't care what did Li Xiaoxi did to you

236
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,840
or how you plan to settle the score.

237
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,320
What I want to know is

238
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,600
do you have another plan?

239
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,670
For what?

240
00:14:15,510 --> 00:14:16,870
Split them up.

241
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:18,480
Sorry, Miss An.

242
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:20,440
I'm honestly done

243
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,320
with this whole thing.

244
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,270
You never intended to help me, did you?

245
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:26,080
You used me as a pawn

246
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:27,440
to take down Li Xiaoxi.

247
00:14:28,090 --> 00:14:28,960
Thanks to you,

248
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:30,630
Bei and I are done for good.

249
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,510
To him, I'm nothing but

250
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:33,790
a scheming troublemaker.

251
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:36,000
Look, if a guy likes you,

252
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:37,630
whatever you do

253
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,800
feels right to him.

254
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:40,750
You and he

255
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,720
were never on the same page.

256
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:48,440
(Divorce Agreement)
I've checked out the venue.

257
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,360
The scale is perfect.

258
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,550
But there are two things to fix.

259
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,270
First,

260
00:14:53,270 --> 00:14:54,910
the runway feels a bit too low.

261
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:56,750
(Marriage/Divorce Registry)
Oh, one more thing.

262
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:59,150
I feel like the current backdrop is cluttered.

263
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:01,670
Could you please talk to

264
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:02,870
the set designer and see

265
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:03,840
if we can strip away

266
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:05,030
some of the extra elements?

267
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,960
Sure. No problem.

268
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,360
Okay.

269
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,270
I'll be there this afternoon.

270
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:13,390
Number H2005, counter two, please.

271
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:19,120
Number B2009, counter five, please.

272
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:25,480
Number B2009, counter five, please.

273
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,320
Xiu?

274
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:28,790
Is that us? B2009?

275
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,700
(Zhongqing District Civil Affairs Bureau,
Marriage Registration Office)

276
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,320
Let's go.

277
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:38,860
(Civil Affairs Bureau)
(Marriage/Divorce Registry)

278
00:15:40,940 --> 00:15:41,780
(Divorce Agreement)

279
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,390
Please confirm.

280
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:46,030
The 30-day cooling-off period's over.

281
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:47,150
You still wish to proceed.

282
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:48,790
Mutual consent to the agreement.

283
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,270
No objections to any terms. Correct?

284
00:15:50,470 --> 00:15:51,310
Yes.

285
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,160
Yes.

286
00:15:52,170 --> 00:15:53,030
Bring the ID photos?

287
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:53,900
Hand them over.

288
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,150
ID photos?

289
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:13,140
(This copy matches the archive.
Holder: Gu Xiu)

290
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:16,900
(Divorce Certificate)

291
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,110
Thanks.

292
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:37,020
(Two hands in marriage, one life together.)
(Marriage is a choice; commitment is a duty.)

293
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:50,510
Do you remember this place?

294
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:54,960
When we first came here,

295
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:58,870
I showed up in front of you,

296
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,960
holding a necklace.

297
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,040
(Miss Yu!)

298
00:17:06,790 --> 00:17:07,680
(What's this about?)

299
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:08,910
This is for you.

300
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:11,680
What is this?

301
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:13,200
It's a unicorn.

302
00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:15,310
It stands for loyalty in love.

303
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:19,000
Anyway, starting now,
I'm done calling you Miss Yu.

304
00:17:19,350 --> 00:17:20,720
I want to call you Yu,

305
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,030
just Yu.

306
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,750
Or Babe, whatever works,

307
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,790
but not Miss Yu.

308
00:17:25,590 --> 00:17:26,880
What's gotten into you?

309
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:30,350
I like you.

310
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:31,640
I want us to be together.

311
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:35,750
You were such a brat.

312
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:39,590
Your tears right now

313
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,480
prove that our marriage

314
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:44,030
wasn't a complete waste.

315
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,400
Maybe I'm not a total failure after all.

316
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:51,590
I'm the one who failed.

317
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,640
Is there even a point

318
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:57,270
in arguing about this now?

319
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,040
I mean it.

320
00:18:01,270 --> 00:18:02,110
It's all my fault.

321
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:05,720
I messed everything up.

322
00:18:12,030 --> 00:18:13,030
In this world,

323
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:16,000
I'm still someone who wants you to be happy,

324
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:19,550
even if we're divorced now.

325
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,790
Give yourself some time.

326
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:25,750
Things will get better.

327
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:34,750
Be with those who love you.

328
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,510
Enjoy your stage.

329
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,070
That'll be a fulfilling way to live.

330
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,800
Remember this.

331
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,720
When you fall in love again,

332
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,270
don't hold back.

333
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:49,830
If you love them, give them your all.

334
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:51,670
If you don't,

335
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,920
don't let it drag on.

336
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,240
From now on, let's not

337
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:09,550
see each other again.

338
00:19:26,660 --> 00:19:32,620
(Divorce Certificate)

339
00:19:33,030 --> 00:19:33,880
Technically,

340
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,740
(Industrial Park Property Lease Agreement)

341
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:36,880
This is your private matter.
I shouldn't interfere.

342
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,270
(Qian Chang Photography Studio)

343
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:40,920
But everyone out there is talking about it now.

344
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,880
They're saying we've got a...

345
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:50,950
I think

346
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,680
you should move out soon.

347
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,830
But I signed a lease for five years.

348
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,480
Yeah, I know.

349
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,000
But now,

350
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,110
your situation's affecting

351
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:01,680
other businesses in the park.

352
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:03,880
Because of this,

353
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,240
I'm getting complaints all day long.

354
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,030
Cut me some slack, okay?

355
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:09,200
I just renovated this place two months ago.

356
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,750
I put over a hundred thousand yuan into it.

357
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:13,510
I can't possibly move out,
even under the lease.

358
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,680
If we go strictly by the lease,

359
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,240
then I've got no argument.

360
00:20:17,050 --> 00:20:17,920
But,

361
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,270
the shops next door

362
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:20,920
are maternity stores

363
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:22,510
and kids' training centers.

364
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,200
Their customers are

365
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:26,000
middle-aged women with families and careers.

366
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:27,880
Your current situation

367
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:30,240
is taking a real toll on them.

368
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:31,960
They complain constantly.

369
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:34,110
Try to see it from

370
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:35,200
their perspective.

371
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,960
I can't think about that right now.

372
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:38,440
I've invested too much here.

373
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,830
And what about my side?

374
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:45,350
Honestly,

375
00:20:46,110 --> 00:20:46,950
business success comes

376
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:48,640
down to the right vibes.

377
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:51,640
But you've messed it up here.

378
00:20:52,510 --> 00:20:53,960
You're not just losing money.

379
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:56,160
You're dragging everyone down with you.

380
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,680
Please move out as soon as possible.

381
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:04,840
Otherwise,

382
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:06,030
I'll be in a tough spot.

383
00:21:06,550 --> 00:21:07,390
Okay.

384
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,720
Mingming,

385
00:21:17,240 --> 00:21:20,200
I know it's not the best time for this,

386
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:23,480
but our pay from last month...

387
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,320
Oh.

388
00:21:24,590 --> 00:21:25,430
Your salary, right.

389
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:27,000
Sorry, I'll go check

390
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:28,000
and wire it over to you.

391
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,550
That's not what I meant, Mingming.

392
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,920
I have a friend working
at a photo studio downtown.

393
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:37,160
They're hiring right now.

394
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,350
So I was thinking…

395
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,240
Mm.

396
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,480
Alright, I get it.

397
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:45,790
Thanks for your hard work here.

398
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,000
Go ahead.

399
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:59,180
(Lease Agreement)

400
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:10,920
Her face shape is a great fit,

401
00:22:11,110 --> 00:22:12,630
you know. Come in.

402
00:22:13,070 --> 00:22:14,510
The lighting here looks...

403
00:22:14,510 --> 00:22:15,510
- Mr. Chen.
- Yeah.

404
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:17,910
Hi, Sen.

405
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,560
Do you need something?

406
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:22,590
Hi, Mr. Cao.

407
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,480
Mr. Chen, I should go.

408
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:25,370
No need.

409
00:22:25,370 --> 00:22:26,240
Just stay.

410
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,080
What's up?

411
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:32,110
I brought some documents.

412
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:34,680
We've finished the design proposal.

413
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,440
Please take a look.

414
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,280
Alright.

415
00:22:37,550 --> 00:22:38,790
Leave it here. I'll check later.

416
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:39,840
Go back to your work.

417
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:43,350
Maybe check it now?

418
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,720
If there's any issue,

419
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,750
I can fix it now.

420
00:22:46,110 --> 00:22:47,000
Just leave it here.

421
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:49,000
I'll check it later.

422
00:22:57,030 --> 00:22:57,870
Get out.

423
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,320
Okay.

424
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,680
What a coincidence.

425
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:12,240
Are you done yet?

426
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,400
Never seen a woman before?

427
00:23:13,790 --> 00:23:14,830
Go on. Keep staring.

428
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:16,750
I'm right here. Go for it.

429
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,510
Sen, calm down.

430
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:19,680
Mr. Cao knows

431
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,590
this photo didn't come from us, right?

432
00:23:21,790 --> 00:23:22,830
We're just looking.

433
00:23:22,830 --> 00:23:23,750
What's the crime in that?

434
00:23:23,750 --> 00:23:24,590
That's enough.

435
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,200
Mr. Cao's here, but I have to say it.

436
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,350
If she weren't your girlfriend,

437
00:23:27,350 --> 00:23:28,640
you'd probably be enjoying it.

438
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,160
I'm not as disgusting as you.

439
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:31,550
I'm not as vulgar as you.

440
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,350
Someone throws out some bait,

441
00:23:33,350 --> 00:23:34,770
and you all swarm it like dogs?

442
00:23:34,770 --> 00:23:35,640
Watch your mouth.

443
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:36,510
Got a problem?

444
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:37,350
That's enough.

445
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:38,440
Do you even want this job?

446
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,750
You know what? I don't!

447
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:41,160
I've wanted to quit for a long time!

448
00:23:41,350 --> 00:23:43,160
Having scum like you as my leader

449
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,480
is a total disgrace to me!

450
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:45,520
Get out!

451
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:46,740
Screw you!

452
00:23:56,660 --> 00:24:00,300
(DEMO)(Burn in hell, homewrecker!)
(You little hussy!)(Furious, huh?)

453
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:05,620
(Burn in hell, homewrecker!)

454
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,220
(DEMO)

455
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,240
Who did this?

456
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:17,750
Show yourself!

457
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:19,510
You're the homewreckers!

458
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:21,270
Your whole family are homewreckers!

459
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,510
You're hussies!

460
00:24:22,510 --> 00:24:23,640
You have no shame!

461
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:25,110
All of you, rot in hell!

462
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:33,640
Come on in.

463
00:24:42,170 --> 00:24:43,030
Take this one,

464
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:43,960
this one, and that one.

465
00:24:43,980 --> 00:24:44,830
Got it.

466
00:24:44,830 --> 00:24:46,720
Mom, Yu might still need these.

467
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:49,200
Yu's starting a whole new chapter.

468
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,590
Everything should be brand new.

469
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:52,880
All this junk should've been

470
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:54,480
trashed long ago.

471
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:56,070
I've got two suitcases and a dog.

472
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,310
I'll go once I'm packed.

473
00:24:57,440 --> 00:24:58,680
Do you think leaving with nothing

474
00:24:58,680 --> 00:24:59,720
is something to be proud of?

475
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,200
Am I supposed to thank you?

476
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:03,400
You've wasted enough of her time.

477
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,400
We aren't even asking for damages.

478
00:25:06,550 --> 00:25:07,720
Consider that a courtesy.

479
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,590
Ma'am, what about this coffee table?

480
00:25:09,590 --> 00:25:11,400
Take it. Take anything you see.

481
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:18,030
Are you happy now that Yu and I

482
00:25:18,830 --> 00:25:19,670
ended up like this?

483
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:20,830
What?

484
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:22,750
I've never seen a mother so thrilled

485
00:25:23,270 --> 00:25:24,590
to see her daughter get a divorce.

486
00:25:24,590 --> 00:25:26,160
So what if I am?

487
00:25:26,590 --> 00:25:28,750
This day couldn't have come soon enough.

488
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:30,790
We must've been blind

489
00:25:31,070 --> 00:25:33,350
to ever let our daughter marry you.

490
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:35,790
Now that I've finally kicked this trash out,

491
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:37,640
how could I not be happy?

492
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:39,000
And once you're gone,

493
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,070
not only will I be happy,

494
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:42,000
I'll set off firecrackers to celebrate.

495
00:25:42,180 --> 00:25:43,070
Excuse me.

496
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,310
My daughter's finally

497
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:45,920
done with this nightmare.

498
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:47,550
I hope she stops

499
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:49,350
picking the wrong guys.

500
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:50,560
Now,

501
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:52,440
take your stupid dog

502
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,830
and get out of my sight!

503
00:25:55,830 --> 00:25:56,670
From now on,

504
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:58,920
stay away from Yu.

505
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,830
I never want to see you again.

506
00:26:00,830 --> 00:26:01,670
Go.

507
00:26:02,270 --> 00:26:03,110
Get out.

508
00:26:26,790 --> 00:26:27,630
That one.

509
00:26:38,110 --> 00:26:38,950
Hello?

510
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,480
Hello, Mr. Gong.

511
00:26:40,790 --> 00:26:43,030
I didn't receive the draft
for the next chapter.

512
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:46,480
Really?

513
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:49,030
I'm sure

514
00:26:49,550 --> 00:26:50,680
I sent it.

515
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:53,310
Maybe it's a...

516
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,640
network glitch.

517
00:26:55,310 --> 00:26:56,750
The thing is, I've got a weak signal.

518
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:57,590
I'm not home.

519
00:26:58,310 --> 00:26:59,750
I'll send it again tonight.

520
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,160
Who's there?

521
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:18,480
Oh, wow.

522
00:27:19,790 --> 00:27:21,350
Two days earlier than I expected.

523
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,550
Have you been waiting for this day?

524
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,880
Do I look like I enjoy others' misfortune?

525
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:28,270
After all the ups and downs,

526
00:27:28,510 --> 00:27:31,270
you finally know who's your warmest haven.

527
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,160
Come on in, sweetheart.

528
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:35,310
Actually, two sweethearts.

529
00:27:47,510 --> 00:27:48,680
Anyone else out there?

530
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:22,480
You're awake.

531
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:23,560
Yeah.

532
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,960
You should've slept in.

533
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:26,270
I'll call you when lunch is ready.

534
00:28:26,870 --> 00:28:27,720
It's fine.

535
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:28,560
I've had enough sleep.

536
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:37,110
I found a new recipe online-

537
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:38,440
cheese waterfall hotpot.

538
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:40,070
It's tasty and foolproof.

539
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:40,920
Try it later.

540
00:28:40,930 --> 00:28:41,790
Okay.

541
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:44,840
Oh, right.

542
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:47,200
You said the home Wi-Fi keeps lagging.

543
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:49,200
I got over a hundred movies,

544
00:28:49,550 --> 00:28:50,440
all kinds of genres.

545
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,830
Watch them whenever you want.

546
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:53,280
Okay.

547
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,320
Also...

548
00:29:03,270 --> 00:29:04,240
I swapped the SIM card

549
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,720
in your phone.

550
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:08,030
You won't get those harassing calls anymore.

551
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,040
Thanks.

552
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:12,840
Are you not

553
00:29:13,350 --> 00:29:14,400
working today?

554
00:29:19,070 --> 00:29:20,310
I'm not that busy lately,

555
00:29:20,510 --> 00:29:21,880
so I took some vacation days.

556
00:29:22,550 --> 00:29:24,550
- Oh.
- I can stay home with you

557
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:26,200
watch shows and play some games.

558
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:32,880
I'll plug in the hard drive.

559
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,320
Sen,

560
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,160
I think

561
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:46,790
something's burning.

562
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,480
Well...

563
00:29:58,160 --> 00:29:59,000
It's okay.

564
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:20,310
♪There's this feeling♪

565
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:25,440
♪I love you♪

566
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,440
Sorry, wrong door.

567
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:35,550
♪Can't help loving you, baby♪

568
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:47,880
Whoa!

569
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:53,640
Did a nuclear bomb go off here?

570
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:56,400
No, no, no!

571
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:58,880
I spent all night drawing this!

572
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:01,160
Now it's dog food.

573
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:03,400
What did I do to deserve

574
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:04,750
raising you brats?

575
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,320
You're back.

576
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:12,000
Stop barking.

577
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,680
Or I'll call the animal shelter and have

578
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:14,790
you both taken away!

579
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:16,750
Come on, come on.

580
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:17,720
Let's have a drink.

581
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:19,070
In your dreams!

582
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:57,350
I'm good.

583
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,750
Hey! How did you lose your job?

584
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,040
Uh…

585
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,270
It's my colleague. Gotta take this.

586
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:20,480
I sent the proposal.

587
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,680
What's left to fix?

588
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,640
What proposal?

589
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,270
Cousin,

590
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:28,510
how did you know?

591
00:32:28,830 --> 00:32:30,160
Is it because of that woman?

592
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,750
That shameless piece of work!

593
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,550
I've warned you.

594
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:35,510
She's only a jinx.

595
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:36,640
Now you've lost your job.

596
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:38,000
How will you even survive?

597
00:32:38,270 --> 00:32:39,720
It was my own decision to resign.

598
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:42,160
And I already told you.

599
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,960
When she was with her ex,

600
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:45,350
she had no idea he was married.

601
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:47,480
And she's not the kind of person you think.

602
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,550
She's a good person.

603
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:49,480
A good person?

604
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:51,030
Does a good person strip down

605
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:52,000
for photos?

606
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:54,550
What kind of spell did she cast on you?

607
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,350
You're still defending her now?

608
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:58,000
Break up with her. End of story.

609
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:58,960
Break up with her now!

610
00:32:58,960 --> 00:32:59,800
This is my...

611
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:02,200
This is my life.

612
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:03,350
I'll handle it myself.

613
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:04,320
Bye.

614
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:13,350
Hello, Mom. What's up?

615
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,680
I can't take this anymore!

616
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:16,640
My son is being played for a fool

617
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,480
and he's just taking it!

618
00:33:18,790 --> 00:33:19,750
How am I supposed

619
00:33:19,750 --> 00:33:21,160
to show my face?

620
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,310
Mom, don't start.

621
00:33:23,270 --> 00:33:24,110
Just tell me,

622
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,240
what should I do?

623
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,400
Leave that woman!

624
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:28,590
Apologize to your boss and go back to work.

625
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:29,480
I'm not going back.

626
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:30,960
I said I'm not going back.

627
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:31,920
Leave me alone!

628
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:37,150
♪You're the only way♪

629
00:33:50,310 --> 00:33:52,070
They're bugging me about every little thing.

630
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:52,910
So annoying.

631
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:56,920
I told them to handle it themselves.

632
00:33:57,350 --> 00:33:58,960
I'm on vacation anyway.

633
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:03,240
What did I miss?

634
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,680
Let me rewind.

635
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:09,320
♪You know what I'll say♪

636
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:21,120
It's only when things

637
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,360
hit the fan, that we realize

638
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,920
what actually matters.

639
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:26,840
You guys all know

640
00:34:27,510 --> 00:34:29,000
what's been going on with Mingming,

641
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:30,510
my girlfriend

642
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:31,670
and future wife.

643
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:35,880
Her photos are everywhere.
People call her a homewrecker.

644
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:38,150
They whisper and point wherever she goes.

645
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:41,150
Back then, I couldn't stand it.

646
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:43,630
I hated even hearing

647
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:45,630
her ex-boyfriend's name.

648
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,510
But now, I've figured it out.

649
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:50,280
None of that

650
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,360
is a big deal.

651
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:55,110
I just want her to be happy.

652
00:34:55,280 --> 00:34:57,030
That's all that matters.

653
00:34:58,920 --> 00:34:59,760
Guys,

654
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:02,320
let me ask you.

655
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:05,760
If you were in my shoes,

656
00:35:06,550 --> 00:35:07,390
what would you do?

657
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:09,910
Gong.

658
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:12,070
Gong?

659
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:15,230
If it were you, how would you handle it?

660
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,510
Beat it.

661
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:23,590
Your drama is not my business.

662
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:25,190
I'm pure-hearted.

663
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:27,510
You're full of tricks.

664
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:29,510
Can you give me some advance?

665
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:31,630
Call me "Dad" first, then we'll talk.

666
00:35:36,810 --> 00:35:37,670
Come on, man.

667
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:39,630
Knowing him,

668
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:43,360
if anyone talked trash,

669
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:44,280
he'd be at their doors

670
00:35:44,630 --> 00:35:46,880
in a heartbeat for a face-off.

671
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:51,670
Is that really what you think?

672
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:54,030
Stop drinking. Stop eating.

673
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:57,880
That's exactly what we think.

674
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,110
I bet

675
00:36:00,110 --> 00:36:00,950
he'd be like this-

676
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,150
"You dare talk smack about my girl?

677
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,280
Not on my watch.

678
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:08,070
You're not getting off easy."

679
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,920
He'd demand an explanation

680
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:11,800
and an apology.

681
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:13,840
That's enough, you guys.

682
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:16,960
I'm not an idiot.

683
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,320
I checked the law.

684
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,670
If they're spreading rumors online,

685
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:23,480
you gather evidence and call the cops.

686
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:27,150
Keep up with the times, will you?

687
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,190
I know that. I already called the cops.

688
00:36:32,070 --> 00:36:33,280
The culprits are in custody.

689
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:34,960
But the people around us

690
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:35,920
didn't break laws.

691
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:37,320
Gossip spreads.

692
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,480
Rumors can drown you.

693
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:40,710
I don't care what they say,

694
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:41,710
but my parents will.

695
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:47,350
What?

696
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:48,470
What?

697
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:50,590
Just answer me.

698
00:36:50,590 --> 00:36:52,320
Do you still want to be with Mingming?

699
00:36:52,320 --> 00:36:53,160
Of course I do.

700
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,360
There's your answer.

701
00:36:55,550 --> 00:36:56,670
Don't be like me,

702
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:58,190
regretting it after she's gone.

703
00:36:58,590 --> 00:36:59,430
Well said!

704
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,360
I've been busy scolding you lately.

705
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:05,440
I forgot to say congrats.

706
00:37:06,230 --> 00:37:07,550
Welcome back

707
00:37:07,710 --> 00:37:09,510
to the Bachelor Club.

708
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:11,760
Why are you chiming in?

709
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,630
From now on,

710
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,400
I'm the Captain,

711
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:16,960
and you're the crew.

712
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:18,190
Mocking me now?

713
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:20,590
There's nothing to celebrate.

714
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:21,880
Who said his marriage

715
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,280
was a total nightmare?

716
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:24,230
Who was that?

717
00:37:24,230 --> 00:37:26,670
None of you have been married.
You wouldn't get it.

718
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:30,030
Marriage, to me now,

719
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:31,360
is kind of like...

720
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:32,800
It's...

721
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:35,710
a trouble I'm not willing to get rid of.

722
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,440
I've never believed in those

723
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,510
"everything happens for the best"

724
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:49,510
empty platitudes.

725
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:51,360
I only believe

726
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:52,880
that you guys

727
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:55,880
will give yourselves the best you can.

728
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,280
Just like you

729
00:37:59,030 --> 00:38:01,000
closing this chapter.

730
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:03,110
You should be happy for yourself,

731
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:05,510
and even happier for Yu.

732
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:06,590
I know.

733
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:09,480
But I... I honestly feel awful.

734
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:12,920
Don't think I'm being dramatic. I...

735
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,630
I really could die for her.

736
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:16,230
I don't want to lose her, really.

737
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:17,230
You're not being dramatic.

738
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:18,950
See?

739
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,070
You cheated on her,

740
00:38:20,070 --> 00:38:22,550
yet you'd give everything for her.

741
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:24,280
Tell me, isn't that love?

742
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:27,070
This is

743
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:31,150
human nature at its most complicated.

744
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:39,400
Guys,

745
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,240
I gotta go.

746
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:41,960
Mingming's home alone.

747
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:43,190
I need to get back.

748
00:38:44,890 --> 00:38:45,760
Catch you later.

749
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:47,110
Can you get the check?

750
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,150
I paid for food.

751
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:51,000
Weren't you paying?

752
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:55,680
See you.

753
00:38:57,110 --> 00:38:57,950
Take care.

754
00:38:58,230 --> 00:38:59,070
Bye, Bei.

755
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:01,160
See you.

756
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:04,030
You leaving?

757
00:39:05,630 --> 00:39:06,670
I'm gonna stick around a bit.

758
00:39:06,670 --> 00:39:07,550
Alright, I'm out.

759
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:09,150
Where are you going?

760
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:10,630
Your live here!

761
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:12,150
Nobody's waiting for me.

762
00:39:12,470 --> 00:39:13,320
Nowhere to call home.

763
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:15,110
Wherever the drinks are, that's where I'll be.

764
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:16,720
Look at him.

765
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:19,190
Must be nice being young.

766
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:20,760
Still got the energy to fool around this late.

767
00:39:21,470 --> 00:39:22,360
Keep it up.

768
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,230
Bye, bye.

769
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:24,070
Bye.

770
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,550
Didn't expect Sen to be so tough.

771
00:39:33,110 --> 00:39:34,360
I thought he'd break.

772
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:36,350
That's just

773
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:38,590
the magic of love.

774
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:41,000
It makes people weak

775
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,600
and miserable,

776
00:39:44,360 --> 00:39:46,150
but it also makes you brave.

777
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:48,670
There's nothing you can't get past.

778
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,030
Yeah, right.

779
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:54,280
Your parents came by, right?

780
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,120
I didn't see them.

781
00:39:56,190 --> 00:39:57,800
They came early and already left.

782
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:01,150
Did you fight with your dad again?

783
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,000
You know his temper.

784
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,590
He used to wail on me when I was a kid.

785
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:09,000
Now he can't beat me anymore,

786
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:10,840
so he nags instead.

787
00:40:12,510 --> 00:40:13,670
Whenever I see him,

788
00:40:13,670 --> 00:40:14,510
if we're not arguing,

789
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:15,510
it feels weird.

790
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:16,550
I wonder

791
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:19,510
how my mom put up with him all these years.

792
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,590
At least your house is lively.

793
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,030
That's not lively.

794
00:40:24,190 --> 00:40:26,000
It's just one fight after another.

795
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:28,630
I don't get it.

796
00:40:28,630 --> 00:40:31,070
Why didn't they divorce back then?

797
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,360
Live their own lives.

798
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:34,480
Why keep torturing each other?

799
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:36,230
Do you even hear yourself?

800
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:38,550
No kid wants their parents to split.

801
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:41,880
I was actually pretty happy as a kid.

802
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,590
I was always at your place.

803
00:40:44,230 --> 00:40:45,710
Your parents never turned me away.

804
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:47,920
Looking back now,

805
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,070
having a friend like you was great.

806
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:54,360
You finally realized?

807
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:56,030
Your parents are good people.

808
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,070
You're not.

809
00:40:57,070 --> 00:40:58,000
Get out of here.

810
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:08,260
(Li Xiaoxi)

811
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,120
(Going to bed?)

812
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:11,280
(I want to talk.)

813
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,670
You...

814
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:15,640
Still not leaving?

815
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:18,920
Someone's waiting for you at home.

816
00:41:19,230 --> 00:41:20,070
(It's late.)

817
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:21,390
(Get some rest.)

818
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:23,960
You were awfully quiet just now.

819
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:25,510
What's bothering you now?

820
00:41:25,800 --> 00:41:26,640
(Good night.)

821
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:30,800
Did you two

822
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:31,870
have a fight?

823
00:41:32,510 --> 00:41:33,740
Are you concerned about me

824
00:41:33,750 --> 00:41:34,670
or Li Xiaoxi?

825
00:41:35,510 --> 00:41:36,960
Isn't that the same thing?

826
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:42,710
I'm a loyal fan of your comics.

827
00:41:43,630 --> 00:41:44,470
Never missed a chapter.

828
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,710
You hid that well.

829
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:50,440
Oh, please. How long have you been a fan?

830
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:52,550
Shou Gongyuan...

831
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:53,950
That's you, right?

832
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:55,800
Hardcore fan!

833
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:56,840
Want an autograph?

834
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,920
I'll sign it for you now.

835
00:41:58,440 --> 00:41:59,840
Princess Ximei

836
00:42:00,630 --> 00:42:02,670
turns into a witch every night.

837
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:05,550
Only the demon Shou Gongyuan knows her secret.

838
00:42:07,230 --> 00:42:08,510
The "Xi" in Ximei

839
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:09,710
is the "Xi" in Li Xiaoxi.

840
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:10,840
Am I right?

841
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,360
Got nothing to say about that?

842
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:28,510
What do you want me to say?

843
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,440
Jiang Yifan is Li Xiaoxi.

844
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:33,800
I like Jiang Yifan,

845
00:42:34,070 --> 00:42:35,280
but I like Li Xiaoxi even more.

846
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:43,320
Don't get the wrong idea.

847
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:45,710
It has nothing to do with either of you.

848
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:46,960
That's my own business.

849
00:42:47,630 --> 00:42:48,670
Jiang Yifan,

850
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:51,030
to me, feels more like a dream.

851
00:42:53,230 --> 00:42:55,110
But as for Li Xiaoxi,

852
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:58,550
at best, I'm just a not-too-bad friend.

853
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:04,670
If you're bitter about this

854
00:43:04,670 --> 00:43:05,510
and take it out

855
00:43:05,510 --> 00:43:06,760
on Li Xiaoxi,

856
00:43:07,030 --> 00:43:08,150
I'll have zero respect for you.

857
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:14,320
Fine.

858
00:43:15,710 --> 00:43:17,150
Remember what you said.

859
00:43:18,230 --> 00:43:19,150
Be her good friend.

860
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:23,760
Let's get one more thing straight.

861
00:43:25,230 --> 00:43:26,480
Why did you hit Lin Chen?

862
00:43:29,150 --> 00:43:30,070
None of your business.

863
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:33,000
You should remember your place.

864
00:43:33,960 --> 00:43:36,920
You're the one who's marrying Li Xiaoxi.

865
00:43:37,630 --> 00:43:39,190
You can't let her get hurt.

866
00:43:39,550 --> 00:43:41,360
Mind your own business first, okay?

867
00:43:42,710 --> 00:43:44,000
What do you know about Li Xiaoxi?

868
00:43:44,670 --> 00:43:46,320
You think you understand her best?

869
00:43:46,710 --> 00:43:48,030
The "platonic male bestie"

870
00:43:48,030 --> 00:43:49,230
staying by her side?

871
00:43:49,630 --> 00:43:50,480
You think that

872
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:51,840
lasts longer.

873
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:54,190
You're obsessed with

874
00:43:54,360 --> 00:43:55,200
this pure kind of love.

875
00:43:55,590 --> 00:43:56,760
You're afraid that if you're together,

876
00:43:57,070 --> 00:43:58,150
it won't be pure.

877
00:43:59,510 --> 00:44:01,070
Your love is nothing special.

878
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:02,240
How could you judge me?

879
00:44:05,110 --> 00:44:06,190
What are you afraid of?

880
00:44:07,760 --> 00:44:08,600
What am I afraid of?

881
00:44:10,480 --> 00:44:11,480
You tell me.

882
00:44:11,480 --> 00:44:12,590
How would I know?

883
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:14,160
I'm not afraid.

884
00:44:14,160 --> 00:44:15,700
(Mom)

885
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:17,160
Hello, Mom.

886
00:44:17,630 --> 00:44:18,670
Emergency with your dad.

887
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:20,550
Get over here, now.

888
00:44:28,960 --> 00:44:31,559
♪I'll admit♪

889
00:44:31,560 --> 00:44:35,599
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

890
00:44:36,480 --> 00:44:40,346
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

891
00:44:40,371 --> 00:44:44,559
♪For this feeling to have you♪

892
00:44:44,840 --> 00:44:47,039
♪I'll resist♪

893
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,374
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

894
00:44:49,399 --> 00:44:51,559
♪Your touches again♪

895
00:44:52,440 --> 00:44:56,420
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

896
00:44:56,445 --> 00:44:59,479
♪For an image of you♪

897
00:45:00,480 --> 00:45:02,919
♪Take my hand again♪

898
00:45:02,920 --> 00:45:04,679
♪Take my mind again♪

899
00:45:04,760 --> 00:45:08,119
♪Break into my heart again♪

900
00:45:08,520 --> 00:45:10,697
♪I'm falling out again♪

901
00:45:10,722 --> 00:45:12,559
♪I'm on my knees again♪

902
00:45:12,560 --> 00:45:16,399
♪To beg for the truth♪

903
00:45:18,240 --> 00:45:22,399
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

904
00:45:22,400 --> 00:45:27,399
♪Is that the secret to love♪

905
00:45:27,760 --> 00:45:30,719
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

906
00:45:30,800 --> 00:45:34,199
♪Did it come from above♪

907
00:45:34,280 --> 00:45:38,039
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

908
00:45:38,280 --> 00:45:43,359
♪Is that the secret to love♪

909
00:45:43,760 --> 00:45:46,199
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

910
00:45:46,200 --> 00:45:50,639
♪This secret of love♪
